@node selecttile "Select the current tile"

@{b}@{u}@| Player/Exit/Platform/Block etc.@{ub}@{uu}

Use this cycle gadget to change the current tile that you are pasting onto
the map.
When you select the teleport tile you will be asked if you wish to set the
teleport destination, if you select yes then the next square of the map
that you click on will become the new teleport destination. You can then
paste down as many teleports as you want but they will all teleport to the
same destination. To change the destination select the teleport tile again
using this cycle gadget.

